UPDATE audits
SET executive_summary = '{"text":"Your account already has a solid revenue base in **Evergreen New Subscriber Flow**, **MM | Cart Abandonment**, and **MM | Abandoned Checkout**, which together drive about **$4.2K** of the roughly **$4.9K** in named flow revenue we reviewed. The biggest upside now is consolidating the fragmented **subscription upsell** setup and adding missing **Post-Purchase**, **Winback**, and **Back-in-Stock** flows so more first-time buyers turn into repeat and subscription customers.","strengths":["**Welcome and recovery flows are the backbone of the account**, **Evergreen New Subscriber Flow** generated **$2,159.64**, **MM | Cart Abandonment** generated **$1,055.19**, and **MM | Abandoned Checkout** generated **$978.78**, or about **86%** of the named flow revenue reviewed.","**Cart recovery is established and converting**, **MM | Cart Abandonment** converted at **1.32%** from **908 recipients** and **MM | Abandoned Checkout** converted at **1.31%** from **1,084 recipients**, which is a healthy starting point for optimization.","**SMS is already active in key moments**, **MM | SMS - Welcome Flow** produced **$440.58** at a **2.09%** conversion rate and **MM | SMS - Browse Abandonment** produced **$157.39** at a **2.73%** conversion rate.","**Subscription upsell motion already exists**, **First Time Customer > Subscription Upsell** has already generated **$635** and **MM | SMS - Subscription Up-Sell Flow** is live, which is important for a subscription-led brand.","**This is a mature Klaviyo setup, not a starter account**, you already have **46 flows**, **600 campaigns**, **50 segments**, and **33 forms**, so the main opportunity is tightening and consolidating rather than building from scratch."],"concerns":["**Subscription lifecycle is fragmented right now**, you have multiple draft flows sitting idle, including **Nightcap Drops to Gummy Subscription**, **Detox Enzyme Subscription Upsell (8.11.23)**, **Nightcap Gummy > Subscription**, **Gut Therapy Subscription Upsell**, and **Night Gummy Subscription Push**, while **MM | Subscription Upsell** is still manual.","**Your highest-volume welcome flow is under-converting**, **Evergreen New Subscriber Flow** reached **24,891 recipients** but converted at just **0.15%**, which is low for the amount of traffic entering it.","**SMS cart recovery is not pulling its weight yet**, **MM | SMS Cart Abandonment** has **45 recipients** and **$0** in revenue, and **MM | SMS - Checkout Abandonment** has only **$78.86** from **90 recipients**.","**We did not find a live Post-Purchase revenue flow in the current setup**, which is a major gap because first-time buyers are not being systematically pushed into second purchase, replenishment, or subscription.","**We did not find a live Winback or Re-engagement flow in the current setup**, so lapsed one-time buyers and churned subscribers are likely relying on regular campaigns instead of a dedicated recovery sequence.","**Account sprawl is becoming a risk**, with **46 flows**, **600 campaigns**, **50 segments**, and **33 forms**, it becomes much easier for overlap, inconsistent offers, and audience fatigue to creep in unless the program is tightly organized."],"timeline":[{"phase":"Phase 1","timeframe":"Week 1-2","label":"Quick Wins","items":["Consolidate the draft subscription flows, starting with **Nightcap Drops to Gummy Subscription**, **Gut Therapy Subscription Upsell**, and **Night Gummy Subscription Push**, and turn **MM | Subscription Upsell** from manual into a proper automated path.","Rewrite and retime **MM | SMS Cart Abandonment** and **MM | SMS - Checkout Abandonment**, because one is at **$0** and the other has produced only **$78.86** so far.","Audit overlap and exclusions between **Evergreen New Subscriber Flow**, **MM | Cart Abandonment**, and **MM | Abandoned Checkout** so shoppers are not getting stacked messages during the same buying window.","Review the **33 forms** against the promise and offer in **Evergreen New Subscriber Flow** so the opt-in experience matches the first conversion push."]},{"phase":"Phase 2","timeframe":"Week 3-6","label":"Core Flows","items":["Build a dedicated **Post-Purchase** series focused on second order conversion, replenishment timing, and moving one-time buyers into subscription.","Launch a **Winback/Re-engagement** flow for lapsed customers and churned subscribers, with separate paths for recent first-time buyers versus past repeat purchasers.","Add a live **Back-in-Stock** flow to capture high-intent demand that currently has no dedicated follow-up in the account.","Rebuild **Evergreen New Subscriber Flow** into a tighter purchase-focused welcome path, since it drives the most volume but is converting at only **0.15%**."]},{"phase":"Phase 3","timeframe":"Month 2-3","label":"Strategic","items":["Use your **50 segments** more aggressively by separating engaged 30-day, 60-day, and 90-day audiences from unengaged subscribers for campaign sends.","Create VIP, high-LTV, active subscriber, and one-time buyer segments so the **600-campaign** calendar can be more targeted and less repetitive.","Run structured tests on subject lines, offer framing, and creative inside **Evergreen New Subscriber Flow**, **MM | Cart Abandonment**, and **MM | Abandoned Checkout**.","Set campaign exclusions so people entering cart, checkout, and subscription conversion flows are not hit with the same promotional message at the same time."]},{"phase":"Phase 4","timeframe":"Month 3+","label":"Long-Term","items":["Build subscription-specific lifecycle messaging around next order timing, skip or pause prevention, and save attempts for at-risk subscribers.","Add replenishment and cross-sell automations by product type so **Post-Purchase** becomes a repeat-purchase engine, not just a thank-you sequence.","Introduce a **Sunset/List Cleaning** flow to protect deliverability over time, especially with an account sending at the scale of **600 campaigns**.","Expand coordinated email and SMS orchestration across **Welcome**, **Browse Abandonment**, **Cart Abandonment**, **Checkout Abandonment**, and subscription upsell so each channel plays a clear role."]}],"findings":["**Subscription lifecycle is fragmented right now**, you have multiple draft flows sitting idle, including **Nightcap Drops to Gummy Subscription**, **Detox Enzyme Subscription Upsell (8.11.23)**, **Nightcap Gummy > Subscription**, **Gut Therapy Subscription Upsell**, and **Night Gummy Subscription Push**, while **MM | Subscription Upsell** is still manual.","**Your highest-volume welcome flow is under-converting**, **Evergreen New Subscriber Flow** reached **24,891 recipients** but converted at just **0.15%**, which is low for the amount of traffic entering it.","**SMS cart recovery is not pulling its weight yet**, **MM | SMS Cart Abandonment** has **45 recipients** and **$0** in revenue, and **MM | SMS - Checkout Abandonment** has only **$78.86** from **90 recipients**.","**We did not find a live Post-Purchase revenue flow in the current setup**, which is a major gap because first-time buyers are not being systematically pushed into second purchase, replenishment, or subscription.","**We did not find a live Winback or Re-engagement flow in the current setup**, so lapsed one-time buyers and churned subscribers are likely relying on regular campaigns instead of a dedicated recovery sequence."]}'
